# 一、fail2ban 的安装及部署方法&#13;
&#13;
## 步骤1. 更新软件源&#13;
&#13;
　　`sudo apt-get update`&#13;
&#13;
## 步骤2. 安装fail2ban&#13;
&#13;
　　`sudo apt-get install -y fail2ban`&#13;
&#13;
## 步骤3. 启动fail2ban服务并设置开机自启&#13;
&#13;
　　`sudo systemctl start fail2ban`&#13;
&#13;
　　`sudo systemctl enable fail2ban`&#13;
&#13;
